imdb.title: Beibî suteppu
imdb.plot: Maruo Eiichirou (Ei-Chan), a first year honor student, one day decides he's unhappy with the way things are and lacks exercise. He finds a flyer for the Tennis Club and decides to check it out. He's instantly captivated by it. Wit...

episodes.title: Fundamentals are the Weakness
episodes.plot: Yu Nabae matches up with Eiichiro and realizes they really are two players that are virtually the same. He realizes that what Eiichiro lacks is experience with the fundamentals, as he has never played anyone like himself.

episodes.title: Duty and Desire
episodes.plot: Eiichiro runs to watch Natsu's match when he learns she is in danger of losing. Afterwards they return to STC where he meets Ryuhei Aoi, a man who will become his new coach.

episodes.title: Eichiro and Natsu
episodes.plot: Eiichiro and Natsu go out on their first date. He learns how important it is for your ego and your subconscious to match up evenly. Coach Ryuhei decides the only way Eiichiro can meet his goals is to go to Florida during the winter break.
